 "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smooth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * L, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that he may sleep in it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a bed; a thing spread to lie, recline,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sit, upon;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Msb;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mihaAdN", "text_ar": "مِهَادٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, A, L, Msb, K;) so called because of its plainness, evenness, or smoothness: (L:) Az says, that the latter word is more comprehensive than the former: (L:) it is applied to the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ground,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "earth;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a plain, an even,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a smooth expanse;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see a verse of Lebeed cited voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xawaAliqu", "text_ar": "خَوَالِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":] (Az, L, K:) and so is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mahodN", "text_ar": "مَهْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K:) some say, that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mahodN", "text_ar": "مَهْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mihaAdN", "text_ar": "مِهَادٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are [originally] two inf. ns., of the same meaning: or that the former is an inf. n., and the latter a simple subst.: or that the former is sing., and the latter pl.: (MF:) the pl. of the former [in common use] is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muhuwdN", "text_ar": "مُهُودٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (L, Msb, K,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mihaAdN", "text_ar": "مِهَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; and of the latter, [pl. of pauc.,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^amohidapN", "tex